Package org.unibl.etf.epj2.vehicles

Class ElectricCar

java.lang.Object
org.unibl.etf.epj2.vehicles.Vehicle
org.unibl.etf.epj2.vehicles.ElectricCar
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ElectricCar extends Vehicle
The ElectricCar class represents an electric car, which is a type of vehicle. It extends the Vehicle class and includes additional attributes specific to electric cars, such as the purchase date and a description.

This class also sets the hasPassengerCapacity attribute to true, indicating that electric cars have passenger capacity.

Instances of this class can be used to represent electric cars with specific details, and the class provides methods to access an modify these details.

Author:
Tamara Kosovac
